                <h2 data-i18n="about_mcl">About MCL</h2>
                <p data-i18n="about_mcl_desc">
                    Mahanadi Coalfields Limited (MCL) is one of the major coal producing companies of India. It is a subsidiary of Coal India Limited under the Ministry of Coal, Government of India. MCL is responsible for coal mining and production in the Mahanadi region, contributing significantly to the nation's energy security and industrial growth. The company is committed to sustainable mining practices, community development, and environmental stewardship, ensuring a balance between energy needs and ecological preservation.
